AB  - We introduce AnnoLoom, a tool designed to assist researchers with codebook development, annotation tasks, and evaluation of human vs. AI's annotation results. AnnoLoom contributes to human expert-AI collaboration and its efficacy in the context of using Large Language Models (LLMs) for research involving text-based data. We conducted a cognitive walkthrough to iteratively improve the design of AnnoLoom and discussed the future work. 88th Annual Meeting of the Association for Information Science & Technology | Nov. 14 – 18, 2025 | Washington, DC, USA.
