TI  - Performing an Inductive Thematic Analysis of Semi-Structured Interviews With a Large Language Model: An Exploration and Provocation on the Limits of the Approach
PY  - 2024
T2  - Social Science Computer Review
VL  - 42
IS  - 4
SP  - 997
