TI  - Challenges from LLMs as a Natural Language Based Human-machine Collaborative Tool for Software Development and Evolution
ST  - 大模型: 基于自然交互的人机协同软件开发与演化工具带来的挑战
PY  - 2023
T2  - Ruan Jian Xue Bao/Journal of Software
VL  - 34
IS  - 10
SP  - 4601
EP  - 4606
